@startuml Use Case Diagram

actor Player

usecase "Start Game" as UC1
usecase "Select Story Mode" as UC2
usecase "Select Chapter" as UC3
usecase "Engage in Battle" as UC4
usecase "View Battle Status" as UC5
usecase "Choose and Use Skills" as UC6
usecase "Heal Allies" as UC7
usecase "Choose Next Action" as UC8
usecase "Exit Game" as UC9

Player --> UC1 : initiates
UC1 --> UC2 : includes
UC2 --> UC3 : includes
UC3 --> UC4 : includes
UC4 --> UC6 : includes
UC4 --> UC5 : includes
UC6 --> UC7 : extends
UC4 --> UC8 : includes (after winning)
UC8 --> UC3 : includes (select another chapter)
UC8 --> UC9 : includes (return to menu and exit)
UC1 --> UC9 : includes

note right of UC3
  Player selects a chapter before battle.
end note

note right of UC4
  Player fights mobs in turns.
end note

note right of UC5
  Player checks HP/MP status.
end note

note right of UC6
  Player selects and executes skills (attack, etc.).
end note

note right of UC7
  Player uses healing skills (optional for healers).
end note

note right of UC8
  After winning: Choose to select another chapter or return to menu.
end note

@enduml